* does
	* Crop output
	* reads Uganda wave 2 crop output (2010_AGSEC5A) for the 1st season
	* 3A - 5A are questionaires for the first planting season
	* 3B - 5B are questionaires for the second planting season

* assumes
	* customsave.ado
	* mdesc.ado

* TO DO:
